From: Krijn Soeteman <krijn@ksoeteman.nl>
Date: Tue, 15 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] ath79: add support for Fon Fonera Hub FON2415 (Gramofon)

Voegt ondersteuning toe voor de Fon FON2415 (ook: FON2515A02 / Gramofon),
een cloud-muziekstreamer gebaseerd op de Atheros AR9341 SoC.

Hardware:
  - Atheros AR9341 @ 535MHz
  - 64MB DDR2 RAM
  - 16MB SPI NOR flash (MXIC MX25L128)
  - 2.4GHz WiFi (geïntegreerd)
  - 2x Ethernet via Bi-TEK FM-1024LLF switch
  - AKM AK4430ET audio DAC (toekomstig: I2S)
  - UART: J2 header 115200 8N1

Flash-indeling:
  0x000000 u-boot    128KB
  0x020000 firmware  15.75MB
  0xfe0000 fon_data  64KB
  0xff0000 art       64KB (WiFi-kalibratie)

---
 target/linux/ath79/dts/qca9341_fon_fon2415.dts | 1 +
 target/linux/ath79/image/generic.mk             | 1 +
---

diff --git a/target/linux/ath79/dts/qca9341_fon_fon2415.dts b/target/linux/ath79/dts/qca9341_fon_fon2415.dts
new file mode 120000
index 0000000000..1111111111
--- /dev/null
+++ b/target/linux/ath79/dts/qca9341_fon_fon2415.dts
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+[inhoud van fon2415.dts — zie apart bestand]

diff --git a/target/linux/ath79/image/generic.mk b/target/linux/ath79/image/generic.mk
index 0000000000..1111111111 100644
--- a/target/linux/ath79/image/generic.mk
+++ b/target/linux/ath79/image/generic.mk
@@ -<zoek naar een logische plek, bijv. na andere FON-entries> @@
+
+define Device/fon_fon2415
+  SOC := ar9341
+  DEVICE_VENDOR := Fon
+  DEVICE_MODEL := Fonera Hub FON2415
+  DEVICE_VARIANT := (Gramofon)
+  DEVICE_DTS := qca9341_fon_fon2415
+  DEVICE_DTS_DIR := ../dts
+  IMAGE_SIZE := 15744k
+  KERNEL_SIZE := 2048k
+  IMAGES := sysupgrade.bin factory.bin
+  IMAGE/sysupgrade.bin := append-kernel | append-rootfs | pad-rootfs | check-size | append-metadata
+  IMAGE/factory.bin    := append-kernel | append-rootfs | pad-rootfs | check-size
+  DEVICE_PACKAGES := kmod-ath9k
+endef
+TARGET_DEVICES += fon_fon2415
